CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    fashion_preference VARCHAR(100),
    favorite_designer VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE designer_info (
    designer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    designer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    designer_location VARCHAR(100),
    design_style VARCHAR(50),
    brand_name VARCHAR(50),
    years_active INT
);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
  user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  fashion_style VARCHAR(50),
  favorite_designer VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE fashion_preferences (
  preference_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  style_category VARCHAR(50),
  color_preference VARCHAR(50),
  size_preference VARCHAR(10),
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id)
)

CREATE TABLE favorite_designers (
  designer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  designer_name VARCHAR(50),
  user_id UUID,
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id)
)

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    fashion_preference VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE user_favorites (
    favorite_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    favorite_designer_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (favorite_designer_id) REFERENCES designers(designer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(50),
    fashion_preference VARCHAR(100),
    favorite_designer VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE user_addresses (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    street_address VARCHAR(100),
    city VARCHAR(50),
    state VARCHAR(50),
    country VARCHAR(50),
    postal_code VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE user_orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10,2),
    payment_method VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE designer_info (
    designer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    designer_name VARCHAR(50),
    designer_description TEXT,
    designer_website VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE designer_collections (
    collection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    designer_id INT,
    collection_name VARCHAR(100),
    collection_description TEXT,
    release_date DATE
)
